            "Total loss: 0.0043402864 Scores for real: 0.99655956 Scores for generated: 0.0008768295\n",
            "Total loss: 0.04669003 Scores for real: 0.9937058 Scores for generated: 0.014445845\n",
            "Total loss: 0.0074086864 Scores for real: 0.9927226 Scores for generated: 0.00010457821\n",
            "Total loss: 0.0013395697 Scores for real: 0.99866116 Scores for generated: 1.4081239e-08\n",
            "Total loss: 0.059076376 Scores for real: 0.99894047 Scores for generated: 0.015243756\n",
            "Total loss: 0.0085791545 Scores for real: 0.99145746 Scores for generated: 4.2778964e-08\n",
            "Total loss: 0.014346502 Scores for real: 0.98575586 Scores for generated: 1.4063318e-09\n"
          ],
          "name": "stdout"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "aRjdscyah42K",
        "colab_type": "text"
      },
      "source": [
        "So we have got nearly perfect discriminator that gives 1 for real distribution and 0 for anything else. Let's train generator using such discriminator.\n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "fYwtOf2W7laB",
        "colab_type": "text"
      },
      "source": [
        "## Generator"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "HNeFN2SMRbhw",
        "colab_type": "code",
        "colab": {}
      },
      "source": [
        "def g_loss(x, discriminator=discriminator):\n",
        "  return tf.reduce_mean(1.0-discriminator(x))\n",
        "\n",
        "def train_generator(g_loss, batch_size=64):\n",
        "  g_optimizer = tf.keras.optimizers.Adam(learning_rate=0.05)\n",
        "  generator = tf.keras.layers.Dense(1, activation='tanh')\n",
        "  for i in range(1000):\n",
        "    with tf.GradientTape() as tape:\n",
        "      z = tf.random.normal(shape=[batch_size, 1])\n",
        "      gen = generator(z)\n",
        "      loss = g_loss(gen) \n",
        "      if i % 100 == 0:\n",
        "        print(\"Loss:\", loss.numpy(), \"Generator output: \",tf.reduce_mean(tf.abs(gen)).numpy())\n",
        "      grads = tape.gradient(loss, generator.trainable_variables)\n",
        "      g_optimizer.apply_gradients(zip(grads, generator.trainable_variables))\n",
        "  t = plt.scatter(np.zeros(z.shape), z.numpy(), label=\"True\")\n",
        "  g = plt.scatter(gen.numpy(), z.numpy(), alpha=0.5)\n",
        "  plt.xlim(-1, 1)\n",
        "  plt.legend((t,g),(\"True distribution\", \"Generated distribution\"))  \n"
      ],
      "execution_count": 0,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "CcuO5eW7SKH5",
        "colab_type": "code",
        "outputId": "181b85e7-cc6d-4c0b-9fe9-189af5977179",
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/",
          "height": 449
        }
      },
      "source": [
        "train_generator(g_loss)"
      ],
      "execution_count": 0,
